{
  "stem": "7458.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could see through the cracks what was going on in town-- the crying, the driving of old men and women.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard the shots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were killed right in the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody was driven out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of my family-- my father, my mother, my sister Tzipe, my-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] my sister Feitche, my sister Baile, my niece Roske, and then many non-family members.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Suddenly, after a while, things became quiet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everyone who left for the center of town had left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those who didn't leave, the Germans and the Poles found and shot on the spot, mostly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We could see some of them walking in the street, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and we could-- we could see that and hear that very-- very clearly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could see them quite well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After a while, it was quiet, except that a neighbor of ours-- the same Bolek whose daughter went to get medicine when my father was beaten-- and this Bolek actually worked for my father in the tannery, and we always treated him well.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we thought he was a good neighbor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the minute they liquidated town, he became frantic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wanted our house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he knew that we did not march off to town, so he knew that we were hiding, but he didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he came around with a rifle looking for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then he brought the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, saying, we know that they are there, because they didn't march off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only so-and-so and so-and-so marched off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest of them didn't, so we know that they are here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We've got to find them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We've got to find them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We've got to kill them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he came with-- he had a rifle himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
